Package: shinyAntDesignX
Title: Ant Design X Components for R Shiny
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Kaiping", "Yang", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "kaiping.yang@example.com")
Description: A collection of Shiny htmlwidgets wrapping Ant Design X React components
    for building AI-driven interfaces. Provides 19 independent widgets covering the full
    @ant-design/x component set: XMarkdown (streaming Markdown), CodeHighlighter, Mermaid,
    ThoughtChain, Think, BubbleList, Sender, Attachments, Suggestion, Actions, Sources,
    FileCard, Folder, Conversations, Welcome, Prompts, Notification, XCard (A2UI v0.9
    dynamic card protocol), plus a full AI chat widget (antDesignXOutput) with streaming,
    tool calls, slash commands, and conversation history.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    htmlwidgets,
    jsonlite,
    shiny,
    promises
Suggests:
    devtools,
    base64enc,
